<p>TCNJ Shop Request is an application designed to allow individuals with food insecurities in the Ewing and Mercer County communities to order food while tracking certain nonharmful analytics.</p>

<button class="btn go block margin-auto">
	<%= link_to "Order Food", controller:"orderfood" %>
</button>

